These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, lime, banana, nectarine
4 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, guinea-pig, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, tram, taxi, train
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the person driving the train is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person eating banana is on the far left##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the bird is between the person driving the taxi and the person eating lime##2
6. the person driving the tram is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | banana | nectarine  | lime | cranberry  |
| Pet         | frog    | bird  | hamster       | guinea-pig     |
| Transport   | taxi     | airplane | train       | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, dancing, cooking, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, adventure, drama, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, soccer, ice-hockey
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
5. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person watching drama movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | dancing | rock-climbing    | collecting  | cooking |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | musical  | adventure   | drama    |
| Sport         | skateboarding | ice-hockey | golf | soccer      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, fanta, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, reading, hiking, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, punk, gospel, r&b
1. the fan of punk is between the fan of r&b and the person drinking water##2
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
6. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | water | iced-tea         | soy-milk   | fanta    |
| Hobby         | reading | writing | camping | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | punk        | r&b      | reggae   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, nigerian, canadian, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, soccer, golf, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, train, skateboard, tram
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the tram and the thai##2
3. the canadian is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the canadian is on the right of the egyptian##1
6. the person driving the tram is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person driving the train##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | thai        | nigerian   | egyptian | canadian |
| Sport         | golf | skiing | soccer    | water-polo |
| Transport     | skateboard       | subway     | tram       | train    |

