.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, milk, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, writing, filmmaking, fishing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, parkour, weightlifting, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking cola##2
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | sprite | water      | cola       | milk   |
| Hobby      | camping   | writing  | fishing | filmmaking     |
| Sport      | parkour     | lacrosse | weightlifting        | rowing |

