.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, garlic, eggplant, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, rock-climbing, magic-tricks, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, lacrosse, cycling, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's sport is cycling##2
6. the person eating garlic is between the person eating tomato and the person eating eggplant##2
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | eggplant | garlic  | tomato | strawberry      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | sudoku  | card-games | rock-climbing |
| Sport   | baseball | weightlifting | lacrosse | cycling     |

