.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, cucumber, pumpkin, onion
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, action, time-travel, musical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, parkour, rowing, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is the person watching action movies##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person eating cucumber is between the person watching action movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
7. the person eating onion is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | pumpkin  | cucumber    | onion | pear  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | musical       | action        | comedy    |
| Sport         | parkour | sailing | cricket  | rowing |

