.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, fishing, skydiving, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, horror, romance, disaster
4 different pets are kept: rat, frog, snake, guinea-pig
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person watching horror movies is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | reading  | fishing | skydiving | hiking |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | disaster | horror   | romance         |
| Pet           | rat | snake  | frog   | guinea-pig      |

