The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, rock-climbing, drawing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, electronic, disco, hip-hop
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person eating asparagus##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person eating grapes##1
5. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the fan of disco and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon  | asparagus    | banana | grapes       |
| Hobby         | drawing | board-games | filmmaking  | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | hip-hop      | electronic  | reggae     |

