.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, cauliflower, kiwi, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, photography, traveling, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: horse, fish, frog, chinchilla
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
2. the owner of the frog is the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the owner of the horse and the person eating spinach##2
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is the owner of the fish##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | spinach  | kiwi | tomato | cauliflower     |
| Hobby   | video-games | traveling   | magic-tricks  | photography    |
| Pet     | fish        | chinchilla       | horse      | frog |

