3. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking tea and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | tea     | coffee | fanta       |
| Hobby      | video-games  | cooking | rock-climbing  | dancing |
| Pet        | hedgehog  | fish      | rat        | rabbit      |

