.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, photographer, journalist, electrician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery, animation, horror
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi, skateboard, helicopter
1. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the journalist##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the pilot##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the taxi is between the person watching animation movies and the journalist##2
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the taxi is the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
