.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, traveling, rock-climbing, hiking
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, firefighter, pilot, nurse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, surfing, tennis, soccer
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the nurse##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is between the photographer and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
6. the pilot is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is surfing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing   | traveling           | magic-tricks         | hiking      |
| Job     | photographer | pilot | nurse | firefighter |
| Sport   | tennis     | surfing         | badminton       | soccer        |

