.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, sprite, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, pop, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, pakistani, australian, spanish
1. the fan of electronic is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking sprite and the pakistani##2
3. the person drinking sprite is the fan of gospel##1
4. the person drinking sprite is between the fan of pop and the spanish##2
5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the turkish is between the australian and the fan of classical##2
7. the fan of electronic is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | milk | sprite | juice   | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | gospel    | pop   | classical     |
| Nationality   | spanish  | australian | turkish | pakistani   |

