.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, sprite, milk
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, corn, strawberry, cherry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, biathlon, rowing, parkour
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
2. the person eating strawberry is between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is rowing##2
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
7. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | lemonade | milk           | sprite |
| Food       | pineapple | strawberry    | corn          | cherry   |
| Sport      | rowing  | biathlon   | parkour | climbing  |

