The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, satire, zombie
4 different pets are kept: snake, fish, hamster, pony
1. the person watching satire movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking coffee is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
6. the owner of the pony is between the person drinking almond-milk and the owner of the snake##2
7. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | 7up | coffee | almond-milk     | juice   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | zombie        | satire  | crime  |
| Pet           | snake      | pony         | fish | hamster |

