.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, electrician, videographer, writer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, biathlon, climbing, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, car, train, van
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the videographer##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the chef is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the train is the writer##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the train##1
6. the person driving the van is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person driving the train##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | chef        | writer  | videographer | electrician   |
| Sport       | volleyball | tennis | climbing    | biathlon |
| Transport   | motorbike        | train     | van       | car      |

